de lucide-menu w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></nav></div><main class=\"min-h-screen pt-20\"><div class=\"bg-white min-h-screen relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden opacity-30\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to right, #e4e4e7 1px, transparent 1px),\n            linear-gradient(to bottom, #e4e4e7 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:80px 80px;mask-image:radial-gradient(400px circle at 0px 0px, black, transparent);-webkit-mask-image:radial-gradient(400px circle at 0px 0px, black, transparent)\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to right, #f4f4f5 1px, transparent 1px),\n            linear-gradient(to bottom, #f4f4f5 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:80px 80px\"></div></div><section class=\"section-padding pt-48 pb-32\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.95)\"><span class=\"text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-8 block font-mono\">Our Vision &amp; Goals</span></div><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-[160px] font-bold tracking-tighter mb-12 leading-[0.8] text-black italic-bold\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden py-1 mb-4\"><span class=\"inline-block\" style=\"transform:translateY(100%)\">V</span><span class=\"inline-block\" style=\"transform:translateY(100%)\">I</span><span class=\"inline-block\" style=\"transform:translateY(100%)\">S</span><span class=\"inline-block\" style=\"transform:translateY(100%)\">I</span><span class=\"inline-block\" style=\"transform:translateY(100%)\">O</span><span class=\"inline-block\" style=\"transform:translateY(100%)\">N</span></div><span class=\"text-primary not-italic\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden py-1\"><span class=\"inline-block\" style=\"transform:translateY(100%)\">2</span><span class=\"inline-block\" style=\"transform:translateY(100%)\">0</span><span class=\"inline-block\" style=\"transform:translateY(100%)\">3</span><span class=\"inline-block\" style=\"transform:translateY(100%)\">0</span><span class=\"inline-block\" style=\"transform:translateY(100%)\">.</span></div></span></h1><p class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl text-muted leading-relaxed font-medium max-w-4xl\">Our long-term goal for supporting Turkish graduates worldwide. We are building a future where every alumni has access to global opportunities, professional growth, and a strong community.</p></div></section><section class=\"section-padding py-40 bg-zinc-50/50 border-y border-zinc-100 relative\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:p-12\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"p-6 md:p-12 bg-white border border-border rounded-[60px] hover:border-primary transition-all duration-700 group shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-zinc-50 border border-border rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-700 shadow-xl mb-10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-10 h-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-6 underline decoration-primary/20 group-hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">Alumni Excellence</h3><p class=\"text-muted font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed\">Building a professional community of over 100,000 successful graduates by 2030.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"p-6 md:p-12 bg-white border border-border rounded-[60px] hover:border-primary transition-all duration-700 group shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-zinc-50 border border-border rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-700 shadow-xl mb-10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cpu w-10 h-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M17 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M17 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M2 17h2\"></path><path d=\"M2 7h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 17h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 7h2\"></path><path d=\"M7 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M7 2v2\"></path><rect x=\"4\" y=\"4\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect><rect x=\"8\" y=\"8\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-6 underline decoration-primary/20 group-hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">Career Matching</h3><p class=\"text-muted font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed\">Helping our members find the perfect academic and job opportunities worldwide.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"p-6 md:p-12 bg-white border border-border rounded-[60px] hover:border-primary transition-all duration-700 group shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-zinc-50 border border-border rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-700 shadow-xl mb-10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-10 h-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-6 underline decoration-primary/20 group-hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">Global Reach</h3><p class=\"text-muted font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed\">Establishing local branches and digital groups in every major city across the globe.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section-padding py-40\"><div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:p-24\"><div class=\"flex-1 space-y-12\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tighter leading-tight italic-bold uppercase\">OUR CORE <br/><span class=\"text-primary not-italic\">GOALS.</span></h2><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl text-muted font-medium leading-relaxed\">We are more than a network; we are a community focused on your success. Our 2030 vision uses the talent of our graduates to create a positive impact on technology and global cooperation.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-8 pt-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-black\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-zinc-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border border-border group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-compass w-6 h-6 text-primary group-hover:rotate-45 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m16.24 7.76-1.804 5.411a2 2 0 0 1-1.265 1.265L7.76 16.24l1.804-5.411a2 2 0 0 1 1.265-1.265z\"></path></svg></div>Direction Protocol</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-black\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-zinc-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border border-border group\"><svg xm